<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4632025>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Colobomatus pupa Izawa, 1974, adult female.(A) Habitus, dorsal; (B) habitus, ventral; (C) antennule, ventral; (D) buccal capsule and mouthparts, ventral; (E) leg 1, ventrolateral; (F) leg 2, ventrolateral; (G) leg 3, ventrolateral; (H) ornamentation on fourth pedigerous somite, ventral. Abbreviations: A, antenna; la, labium; mx, maxillule; Mx, maxilla." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4632025/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

